## 1. SmartLinkPoint

### 1.1 Cau[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] truc[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] du[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] lieu[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME]

```
SmartLinkPoint
  cellId: string
  touches: Map<targetCellId, TouchRecord>

TouchRecord
  targetCellId: string
  firstTouchAt: timestamp
  lastTouchAt: timestamp
  touchCount: number
  sensitivity: number        // 0.0 – 1.0
  fiber: boolean             // state flag — khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] stage rieng[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME]
  layers: { signal, context, state, data }
```

### 1.2 Fiber lifecycle

Fiber la[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] **state flag** trong TouchRecord, khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] stage rieng[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] trong lifecycle.

```
Transitions:
  fiber = false → true   khi sensitivity ≥ 0.75  (fiberFormed)
  fiber = true  → false  khi sensitivity ≤ 0.20  (fiberLost)

TouchRecord ton[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] tai[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] tu[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] len[C2:RN_AN_EN] touch dau[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] tien[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] den[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] khi dissolve.
fiberLost KHONG[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] xoa[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] TouchRecord.
dissolve xay[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] ra khi sensitivity < 0.05 → xoa[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] TouchRecord khau[C3:RN_OI_AU] touches Map.
```

### 1.3 Phen[C0:RN_AN_EN] biet[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] fiberLost vs dissolve

| | fiberLost | dissolve |
|---|---|---|
| Trigger | sensitivity ≤ 0.20 | sensitivity < 0.05 |
| Ket[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] qua[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] | fiber = false | TouchRecord bi[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] xoa[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] |
| TouchRecord | ven[C4:RN_AN_EN] ton[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] tai[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] | bi[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] xoa[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] khau[C3:RN_OI_AU] touches Map |
| Co[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] the[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] phuc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] hau[C2:RN_OI_AU] | Co[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] — neu[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] touch lai[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] | Khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] — phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] touch mau[C1:RN_OI_AU] tu[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] dau[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] |

