## 2. SmartLink Decay

### 2.1 Cong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] thuc[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME]

```
decayRate = FIBER_DECAY_RATE_BASE / (1 + touchCount ×[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] FIBER_DECAY_K)
```

**Loai[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] decay:** Saturating (khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] logarithmic, khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] linear)

**Ly[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] do chon[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] saturating:**
- Logarithmic: khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] ve[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] 0 → fiber bat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] tu[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] → he[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] the[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] loai[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] bo[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] pattern cu[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME]
- Linear: decay deu[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] bat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] ke[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] lich[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] su[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] → mat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] gia[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] tri[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] cua[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] pattern da[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] duoc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] reinforce nhieu[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME]
- Saturating: fiber manh[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] decay cham[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] hon[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] nhung[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] ven[C4:RN_AN_EN] co[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] the[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] ve[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] 0

### 2.2 Constants

```typescript
FIBER_DECAY_IDLE_MS   = 7 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000  // 7 ngay[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] idle → decay bat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] dau[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME]
FIBER_DECAY_RATE_BASE = 0.10
FIBER_DECAY_K         = 0.2
FIBER_MIN_SENSITIVITY = 0.20                       // fiberLost threshold (hysteresis)
FIBER_DISSOLVE_THRESHOLD = 0.05                   // dissolve threshold
```

### 2.3 Execution model

```
Decay PHAI[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] chay[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] theo continuous tick.
Decay KHONG[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] DUOC[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] chi[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] chay[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] khi idle check.

Neu[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] chi[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] chay[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] khi idle check → burst decay.
Burst decay lam[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] mat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] tinh[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] lien[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] tuc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] cua[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] temporal memory.
```

### 2.4 Hysteresis

```
fiberFormed tai[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] sensitivity ≥ 0.75
fiberLost   tai[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] sensitivity ≤ 0.20

Khoeng[C3:RN_ANG_ENG] buffer 0.20 – 0.75: fiber khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] dau[C3:RN_OI_AU] treng[C5:RN_ANG_ENG] thai[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME].
Tranh[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] oscillation lien[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] tuc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] khi sensitivity dao dong[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] quanh threshold.
```

