```typescript
interface FiberSummary {
  nodes: [string, string]   // [sourceCell, targetCell]
  strength: number          // = sensitivity tai[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] thau[C2:RN_OI_AU] diem[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] gossip
  ttl: number               // hop count con[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] lai[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME]
}
```

Khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] cen[C2:RN_AN_EN] fiber_id. Cap[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] nodes la[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] dinh[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] danh du[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME].

### 3.2 Gossip triggers — 2 teng[C2:RN_ANG_ENG] (Gatekeeper chot[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME])

```
Teng[C2:RN_ANG_ENG] 1 — nhe[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME]:
  Trigger: touchCount ≥ 2
  ttl: 1
  Muc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] dich[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME]: lan pattern gen[C2:RN_AN_EN] truoc[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] khi fiber hinh[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] thanh[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME]

Teng[C2:RN_ANG_ENG] 2 — manh[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME]:
  Trigger: fiberFormed (sensitivity vua[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] vuot[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] 0.75)
  ttl: 3
  Muc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] dich[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME]: lan pattern da[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] on[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] dinh[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] ra toen[C2:RN_AN_EN] meng[C5:RN_ANG_ENG]
```

**Chua[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] chot[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME]:** fiberWeakening gossip trigger — pending session sau.

### 3.3 Propagation

```
Khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] dung[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] central registry.
Lan qua: SmartLinkCell.getPoint(targetCellId)
Neighbors = cells da[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] co[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] trong touches Map cua[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] cell hien[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] tai[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME].
