### 3.4 receiveGossip logic

```
if incoming.strength > local.sensitivity:
  update local fiber state
if summary.ttl > 0:
  forward(summary vau[C1:RN_OI_AU] ttl--)
```

### 3.5 Constraints

```
gossipQueue: async — khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] block touch() hot path
dedupeCache: chong[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] gossip storm
```

