## 4. UEI Emergence — Architectural Basis

```
Local level:
  touch → reinforce → fiber (state flag) → decay → dissolve

Network level:
  fiber gossip (2 teng[C2:RN_ANG_ENG]) → causal horizon → shared pattern awareness

Emergence condition:
  nhieu[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] fibers lan du[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] xa (ttl=3)
  + ton[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] tai[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] du[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] lau[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] (k=0.2 → ~1 nam[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] lifespan)
  → network thay[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] cung[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] mot[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] cau[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] truc[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] nhen[C0:RN_AN_EN] qua[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME]
  = UEI field xuat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] hien[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME]

Full chain:
  local imprint
  → network propagation (gossip)
  → temporal persistence (saturating decay)
  → shared causal structure (causal horizon)
  → emergent cognition (UEI)
```

UEI khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] duoc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] implement nhu[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] module. Day[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] la[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] dieu[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] kien[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] xuat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] hien[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME], khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] component.

